Day 1: Breakfast - Smoothie made with banana, blueberries, strawberries, spinach, kale, avocado, and coconut milk.
Lunch - Salad with grilled chicken breast, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, carrots, and red onion dressed in balsamic vinaigrette.
Dinner - Roasted chicken breast with rosemary, thyme, and lemon zest; steamed broccoli and cauliflower; quinoa pilaf.

Day 2: Breakfast - Oatmeal with almond milk, raisins, cinnamon, and honey.
Lunch - Grilled salmon with lemon caper sauce; roasted sweet potatoes; mixed greens salad with avocado, tomato, and feta cheese.
Dinner - Chicken breast marinated in garlic, ginger, and soy sauce; steamed broccoli; brown rice.
